  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Mix flaxseed meal and chia seeds in a bowl with rolled oats.",
    "Add almond flour, mixed berries, halved mini tomatoes, chopped onions, minced garlic, olive oil, and chicken or vegetable broth into the oat mixture. Mix well.",
    "Transfer the quiche filling to a greased 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes at 375°F (190°C).",
    "Remove from oven, let cool slightly, and then place under char-grill until charred on top for an additional 4-5 minutes.",
    "Serve warm."
